      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "Democratic proponents of simply raising or repealing the cap have continued to deliberately promote fact-free misinformation about their proposal’s effects, pretending the new deductions would mostly help firefighters, teachers, and other middle-class households. "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            13
