      1,
      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "For his part, Sanders has "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            14
          ],
          1,
          "called"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          " the House-passed proposal “bad policy” and “bad politics” — and his initiative seems designed to make the politics at least a bit better, although his plan is hardly perfect."
        ]
      ]
    ],
    [
      1,
      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "“If you actually cared about (the middle class), you could set the cutoff at say, $150,000,” Marc Goldwein of the Committee For A Responsible Federal Budget "
        ],
        [
          0,
